<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">خ د ر:</span> <span class="c2">(الْخِدْرُ)</span> السِّتْرُ وَجَارِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(مُخَدَّرَةٌ)</span> إِذَا لَزِمَتِ الْخِدْرَ. وَ <span class="c2">(الْخَدَرُ)</span> فِي الرِّجْلِ وَبَابُهُ طَرِبَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>